Package: tweave
Title: Knit R Code into Typst Documents
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("James", "Bruce", email = "CHANGE-ME@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Weaves R code chunks embedded in Typst ('.typ') documents and
    compiles the result to PDF, in the tradition of 'Sweave' and 'knitr'.
    Ships a companion Typst package with a homework template, auto-numbered
    questions, and statistics-flavored math shorthands.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    knitr,
    tools,
    utils
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    withr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
SystemRequirements: Typst CLI (https://typst.app/)
URL: https://github.com/jimna-h/tweave
BugReports: https://github.com/jimna-h/tweave/issues
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
